51.6	Financial_statements	Financial statement	A financial statement (or financial report) is a formal record of the financial activities of a business, person, or other entity. In British English—including United Kingdom company law—a financial statement is often referred to as an account, although the term financial statement is also used, particularly by accountants.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Wachovia_National_Bank_1906_statement.jpg/250px-Wachovia_National_Bank_1906_statement.jpg
